column2: CRYPTO UPDATE All of the largest cryptocurrencies were up during morning trading on Friday, with Polkadot (DOTUSD) seeing the biggest move, rocketing 35.22% to $11.60. Cardano (ADAUSD) soared 22.07% to 58 cents, while Ripple (XRPUSD) jumped 17.
column4: Polkadot leads way as largest cryptocurrencies post advances
